{"tid":611790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"訂造傢俬搞到一肚氣","createTime":"2018-03-31T11:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T15:25:00.000Z","uid":179426,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff296219f1a9a094c639765ff93ac6b42bd515b5","tid":611790,"uid":179426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"本身諗住上大陸造，但睇左好多中伏case，最後都揀左香港公司。間設計公司係屋企人朋友介紹，屋企人就叫咗個設計師上黎度尺，睇下可以點設計得實用啲。大概講低想點放啲傢俬，個設計師就話番去畫張圖再叫我地上去傾。<br />\n<br />\n出左張圖，傾左改嘅位置，個設計師係咁催交訂，根本唔係我想要既圖點解要俾訂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最終俾左幾千蚊做訂金，俾完問題就黎啦，個設計根本唔想改圖，佢覺得自己張圖好正無問題，話我地嘅要求無人咁做或者做唔到，最終咩都無改過。 加櫃桶門把又諸多藉口，話好少人加，又話唔靚。個櫃想造細啲又話唔靚，改都淨係肯改一兩寸，同無改無咩分別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為幅圖唔岩心水，改完又改，搵埋實物圖俾佢參考都話做唔到，佢話用cheap料就做到，但係好快玩完唔會負責。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好啦簡簡單單算搞掂啲設計，咁就開始安排油漆師傅開工。哇個師傅煙剷嚟，講極都要食，仲要好無手尾，搞到個洗手盤好多一舊舊泥。油漆已經搞到一肚火，啲傢私簡直係災難，書櫃唔貼牆，牆邊同頂都有條罅，又甩甩漏漏，一間細房做灰水油漆+做儲物床（唔係地台）+床尾衣櫃+書枱連櫃埋單4萬，搞左舊屎出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/192654_64c058fe62009c3e72b9e9d72bd7ce3b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F192654_64c058fe62009c3e72b9e9d72bd7ce3b.jpeg&h=a7b3b744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/192835_5ec0855885f114657858d2aa7394f12c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F192835_5ec0855885f114657858d2aa7394f12c.jpeg&h=d0c067cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdcc038031580c5d72d13d180d0e13df85cc3f42","tid":611790,"uid":179426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0274647b4ed9e77931831c73823df01421714a24","tid":611790,"uid":17618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"開公司名"},{"pid":"9a889649aeb888bf992049262a03a8184b4b069d","tid":611790,"uid":179426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0274647b4ed9e77931831c73823df01421714a24","tid":611790,"uid":17618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"開公司名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"間公司話會安排補救，要等兩個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有啲地方唔會補得好，如果唔負責任一定會開名"},{"pid":"e058d253293321257d32ee985da6c68b2e5049e4","tid":611790,"uid":117971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"第二幅圖咁核突既，成舊香口膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a094b9ee37e6e4a4b39277914e8815d3a67826","tid":611790,"uid":179426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e058d253293321257d32ee985da6c68b2e5049e4","tid":611790,"uid":117971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"第二幅圖咁核突既，成舊香口膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"係批上牆既泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔識裝修野，呢啲泥可唔可以沖落洗手盤？"}]}